## 网络概览

- **对象** (object_types/): pod.bkn、node.bkn、service.bkn
- **关系** (relation_types/): pod_belongs_node.bkn、service_routes_pod.bkn
- **行动** (action_types/): restart_pod.bkn、cordon_node.bkn
- **风险** (risk_types/): restart_pod_high_risk.bkn
